/-- A Hölder continuous function is uniformly continuous -/
protected theorem uniform_continuous_on (hf : holder_on_with C r f s) (h0 : 0 < r) : uniform_continuous_on f s :=
  by
  refine' emetric.uniform_continuous_on_iff.2 fun ε εpos => _
  have : tendsto (fun d : ennreal => (C : ennreal) * d ^ (r : exprℝ)) ((nhds) 0) ((nhds) 0) :=
    ennreal.tendsto_const_mul_rpow_nhds_zero_of_pos ennreal.coe_ne_top h0
  rcases ennreal.nhds_zero_basis.mem_iff.1 (this (gt_mem_nhds εpos)) with ⟨δ, δ0, H⟩
  exact ⟨δ, δ0, fun x hx y hy h => (hf.edist_le hx hy).trans_lt (H h)⟩
#align uniform_continuous_on uniform_continuous_on
uniform_continuous:
/-- A Hölder continuous function is uniformly continuous -/
protected theorem uniform_continuous (hf : holder_with C r f) (h0 : 0 < r) : uniform_continuous f :=
  uniform_continuous_on_univ.mp <| (hf.holder_on_with univ).uniform_continuous_on h0
#align uniform_continuous uniform_continuous
